  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\">Added</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>​<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-32083\">LCD-32083</a> - Removed Unnecessary Validation:</strong> Removed an unnecessary modsecurity validation that would pollute the logs and obscure useful error messages, improving log readability and the overall debugging experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38978\">LCD-38978</a></strong> <strong>- Fixed Deployment Issue: </strong>Fixed an issue where configuring the web server with an empty custom domain list would cause deployments to fail, increasing the reliability of our deployment process. </li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-39607\">LCD-39607</a></strong> <strong>- Inaccurate Alert Duration Format: </strong>Fixed an issue where the duration of events on the Alerts page was incorrectly formatted as the time since the event occurred.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
